  "body": "Reference: https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/pull/2362\n\nThe `core.BlockChain` interface needs to be refactored in a simpler interface such that mocking the BlockChain becomes a trivial task.\n\nThe `core.BlockChain` struct contains many methods that not necessary belong in the interface itself. It would be ideal for the `BlockChain` to have a **database** like interface that defines methods like `Put`, `Get`, `Has`. \n",
